    • sortPostList

      public java.util.ArrayList<Post> sortPostList​(java.util.ArrayList<Post> postList, int size)
      Returns a list of posts sorted by their date posted with the latest post first. The length of the post returned is determined by the size inputted.
      Parameters:
      postList - An ArrayList of Post objects to be sorted
      size - An integer representing the size of the ArrayList to be returned
      Returns:
      An ArrayList of Post objects that have been sorted according to their date posted
